    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione eius millesimo
                        centesimo LXII, iduus iunii, indictione X. Manifesti sumus nos <persName
                            ref="#people/3235">Bonifatius</persName> et <persName ref="#people/3234"
                            >Buiamonte</persName> germani fili quondam <persName ref="#people/3227"
                            >Uguicioni</persName> et uxoris illorum <persName ref="#people/3237"
                            >Cangniola</persName> filia <persName><name ref="Widuccius"
                                >Guiducci</name></persName> uxor Bonifatii et <persName
                            ref="#people/3236">Giemma</persName> filia <persName><name
                                ref="Aldebrandus">Aldobrandi</name></persName> uxor Buiamonti (…)
                        interrogate a <persName key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name ref="Piculus"
                                >Picculo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudice</rs>, quia per hanc cartulam venditionis vindimus et
                        tradimus in <orgName key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs
                                key="#Hospitals">osspitale</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/3207"
                            >Altipasti</placeName></orgName> idem unam petia terra que est posita a
                            <placeName ref="#places/3210" key="#Rivers #Roads">Puteum
                            Adimaringum</placeName>, ubi <placeName ref="#places/3210"
                            >Vignale</placeName> vocatur (…) cui de una parte est fini terra caput
                        in <rs key="#Rivers">Giusciana</rs>, de secunda parte est finis terra <rs
                            key="#Roads">via publica</rs> currit. De tertia parte est finis terra de
                        ipso ospitele latus et de filii Uguicioni bene terminata. De quarta parte
                        est finis terra <persName ref="#people/3217">Adimari</persName> filii
                        quondam <persName ref="#people/3218">Alberti</persName>. (…)
                            <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: libre viginti et quatuor de bonis de Lucca et
                        di Pisa. (…) <foreign>Pena</foreign>: duppla. (…) Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/3227">Gangalandi</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName ref="#estates/83" key="#Comitatus">florentino</geogName>. Signum
                        manum supradictorum iugalium qui hanc cartulam venditionis sicut supra
                        legitur fieri rogaverunt. Signum manum <rs key="#Priests">presbiteri</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohanni</name></persName>, qui
                        hanc cartula venditionis fieri rogavit. Signa manuum <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Grullus">Grulli</name></persName> filii
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Oddolinus">Hocdolini</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Hugo">Ugui</name></persName> filii
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Odalricus">Odarrichi</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Zoppus Moricti">Zoppi
                            Moricti</name></persName> qui ibidem fuerunt rogatis <rs key="#Witness"
                            >testes</rs>. (S) Ego Picculus <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scriptor
                        post tradita complevi.</ab>
                </div>
